hmm-tests.c:1962:hmm_gup_test:Expected HMM_DMIRROR_PROT_WRITE..
..(2) == m[2] (34)
hmm-tests.c:157:hmm_gup_test:Expected ret (-1) == 0 (0)
hmm-tests.c:157:hmm_gup_test:Expected ret (-1) == 0 (0)
...
==========================================================

 Call Trace:
 <TASK>
 ? sched_clock+0xd/0x20
 ? __lock_acquire.constprop.0+0x120/0x6c0
 ? ktime_get+0x2c/0xd0
